{"tid":438553,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[日本]有無人玩過真人mario kart?","createTime":"2017-10-17T04:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-17T15:17:43.000Z","uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b50160322813a0268d25f595c2c7ae98b3110bca","tid":438553,"uid":66954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:28:32.000Z","msg":"下星期去東京想玩，<br />\n見唔同分店有唔同路線，秋葉原最平<br />\n同行朋友無車牌，毒撚一個人去得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1個鐘係咪都夠玩?<br />\n另外落雨係咪照揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎分享經驗，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94935ca8770583c1f2b89e95c8ca2bcbb299fcf4","tid":438553,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:29:59.000Z","msg":"玩過，朋友撞車死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7122b9a4b56b03f5c5266d1adfdc62315201312","tid":438553,"uid":117821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:49:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩過，朋友撞車死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個朋友都係 比貨車當場撞死左 念起都巧驚驚"},{"pid":"057f7c4a0df63b2dc4273e2ac2fe7944e67db4c7","tid":438553,"uid":37631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T04:57:07.000Z","msg":"樓上班友 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇中龜殼跌落熔岩燒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb67a8a23fcf6afb93b37990fe52179cee31684b","tid":438553,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"巴打都係唔好玩，俾人用紅龜撞痛撚死"},{"pid":"07c2c14ad989ae887fed2c53fb61deb010a89979","tid":438553,"uid":42407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T07:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上班友 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇中龜殼跌落熔岩燒死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nSorry，我掉嫁"},{"pid":"fcc055f7a01f7327efcdb46c9320661cd1355923","tid":438553,"uid":148444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:12:03.000Z","msg":"4月係東京玩過，都係一個人Join(同行家人都冇車牌)<br />\n我BOOK嘅時段仲有另外5個鬼佬一齊玩，有個guide會帶住，會打手勢教你幾時停、幾時cut線、幾時加油，市內大約行40，去台場行彩虹橋都係60左右。日本駕駛者比較禮讓，其實好安全。"},{"pid":"91747f5ebb3da46de3417ab37dd7f7118ae97a6d","tid":438553,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:16:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4月係東京玩過，都係一個人Join(同行家人都冇車牌)<br />\n我BOOK嘅時段仲有另外5個鬼佬一齊玩，有個guide會帶住，會打手勢教你幾時停、幾時cut線、幾時加油，市內大約行40，去台場行彩虹橋都係60左右。日本駕駛者比較禮讓，其實好安全。</blockquote><br />\n冇牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869bf2445e3e4eb6dde98ff9d9b3710e38185b40","tid":438553,"uid":148444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:39:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>下星期去東京想玩，<br />\n見唔同分店有唔同路線，秋葉原最平<br />\n同行朋友無車牌，毒撚一個人去得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1個鐘係咪都夠玩?<br />\n另外落雨係咪照揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎分享經驗，感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我玩左兩個鐘, 好似兩個鐘先會過台場。<br />\n一個鐘係市內多燈位, 燈位停低d路人會歡呼同要求, 都會暗爽下, 但停得太多都會悶, 出台場過橋可以大力俾油, 風景亦都唔錯, 我覺得值得玩埋<br />\n<br />\n頭一個鐘keep住微雨, 冇乜大影響"},{"pid":"d59e0d81f963aa9b2dffc45a23199e83e29b2dd3","tid":438553,"uid":148444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T10:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下星期去東京想玩，<br />\n見唔同分店有唔同路線，秋葉原最平<br />\n同行朋友無車牌，毒撚一個人去得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk